troubleshooting.title: Encounter xcodebuild exited with code '65' and signal 'null'

cause.p: Your .ipa application and/or WebDriverAgent is not signed correctly.

step.cmd: Sign and rebuild the WebDriverAgent XCode project with your developer certificate.
Uncheck Automatically Signing option from WebDriverAgentRunner and select valid provisioning profile (profile displayed as Eligible from the list).D
